2141	When Anzor Gubashev was asked where he had received bruises and wounds on his
2219	wrists and legs, he said he was beaten, according to the newspaper's
2288	transcript.
2309	"Were the beatings recorded when you arrived in prison?"
2375	"Yes," Gubashev responded.
